China Drafts Plan to Reduce Prices of Electric Vehicle Batteries by 2015

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-04-07T02:29:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/china-drafts-plan-to-reduce-prices-of-electric-vehicle-batteries-by-2015.html
China aims to lower the price of
batteries used for electric vehicles to 2 yuan per watt-hour by
2015 and 1.5 yuan a watt-hour by 2020 as part of a stimulus plan
for the alternative energy vehicle industry, Wang Xiaoming, a
research fellow at the Industrial Economics Research Department
of the Development Research Center of the State Council.  Wang participated in the drafting of the plan, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  